  <div class="one-third column">
    <h4 class="myheadings">AV Controller App &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V375</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V475</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V500D</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V575</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V675</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V775</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V1075</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V2073</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V3073</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Transform your smartphone or tablet into a wireless remote control for Yamaha’s range of network receivers and Blu-ray players. Available as a free download, the AV Controller app provides simple, wireless control of all your home entertainment needs.</p>
      <p>Enjoy access to music content stored on a PC, Mac or Network Attached Storage (NAS) device or browse thousands of Internet radio stations from around the world.</p>
      <p>Yamaha’s dedicated tablet version of the app provides even greater flexibility with more information on the screen at any one time.</p>
      <p><img src="images/av-controller-app.jpg" width="100%" alt="AV Controller App"></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">Music Play &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V375</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V475</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V500D</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V575</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V675</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V775</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V1075</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V2073</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V3073</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Yamaha’s Music Play pushes music wirelessly from an iOS or Android device directly to a Yamaha network receiver.</p>
      <p>This is achieved within the Yamaha AV Controller app ensuring the user can still control other features of the receiver such as adjusting the volume or DSP mode.</p>
      <p>Music Play can also be streamed to a second zone by simply turning on Zone 2 and selecting Music Play as the source.</p>
      <p><img src="images/music-play.jpg" width="100%" alt="Music Play"></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">AirPlay &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V375</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V475</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V500D</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V575</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V675</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V775</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V1075</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V2073</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V3073</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>AirPlay enables the streaming of music from a compatible iOS device directly to your Yamaha network receiver.</p>
      <p>This includes but is not limited to streaming of audio from AirPlay enabled apps such as Pandora, YouTube, TuneIn Radio and the Music app on your iOS device. AirPlay also enables streaming of music directly from an iTunes library, regardless of whether that music is stored on a Mac or PC.</p>
      <p><img src="images/airplay.jpg" width="100%" alt="AirPlay"></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">Apple Remote App &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V375</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V475</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V500D</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V575</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V675</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V775</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V1075</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V2073</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V3073</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Apple’s Remote app enables iTunes to be controlled wirelessly from an iPod, iPhone or iPad.</p>
      <p>Access and control an entire iTunes library from anywhere in the home. It allows you to control and stream your music collection to any AirPlayenabled device.</p>
      <p><img src="images/apple-remote-app.jpg" width="100%" alt="Apple Remote App"></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">Music Streaming &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V375</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V475</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V500D</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V575</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V675</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V775</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V1075</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V2073</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V3073</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Music streaming occurs when digital audio files are accessed from a remote source such as a home computer or smartphone, and played back via a device such as a Yamaha network receiver.</p>
      <p>Yamaha network receivers allow streaming of various music file formats including FLAC, MP3, WAV, WMA and AAC.</p>
      <p><img src="images/music-streaming.jpg" width="100%" alt="Music Streaming"></p>
    </div>
