      <br>
      <p>Wirelessly connect your AV receiver or home theatre package to the home network via WiFi using Yamaha’s YWA-10 wireless adaptor.</p>
      <p>Simply configure the YWA-10 to work with your home network router and plug in your receiver and Blu-ray player via Ethernet.</p>
      <p><img src="images/wifi-adaptor.jpg" width="100%" alt="WiFi Adaptor"></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">Pandora® Internet Radio &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V375</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V475</td>
