      <p>Yamaha’s range of Blu-ray players not only stream music but can also stream 1080p quality video with HD Audio directly from a PC, Mac or Network Attached Storage (NAS) device.</p>
      <p><em>*Yamaha BD-S473 or BD-S673 required</em></p>
      <p><img src="images/video-streaming.jpg" width="100%" alt="Video Streaming"></p>
