      <br>
      <p>Yamaha’s network-enabled AV receivers and Blu-ray players can be easily updated to include the latest firmware and enhancements.</p>
      <p>Connect the device to the Internet and update the firmware directly from Yamaha’s servers.</p>
      <p><img src="images/network-firmware-updates.jpg" width="100%" alt="Network Firmware Updates"></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">Web Browser Control &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V375</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V475</td>
